data.description: Golf Hammock Pool Home on Large Lot with Stunning Water Views!  With Tons of Square Footage, This Spacious 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath Home is Set-Up Perfectly to Bring Out the Entertainer in You.  You Will Enter into a Large Living / Family Area, Complete with a Formal Dining Space That has Sight Lines that Pass All the Way Through the Large Covered Back Porch to the Immense Caged, In-Ground Pool.  Just Around the Corner is a Large Kitchen Area w/ Solid Surface Counter Tops, Tons of Cabinet Space, Cozy Breakfast Nook and an Additional Living Area.  This Split Floor Plan Sets Up Perfectly to Have an Office, Nursery or 4th Bedroom on the Master Bedroom Side and the Massive Master is Complete with Access to the Pool Area and a Large Bathroom, Including Dual Sink Vanity, Separate Tub / Shower and Private Enclosed Toilet Area.  The Remaining Bedrooms are Spacious and the Attached 1/2 Bath Offers Additional Entry to Pool Area.  The Oversized Garage has a Separate Side Entry for Your Golf Cart Which Will be Perfect for you to Explore This Wonderful Neighborhood that Surrounds a Challenging, Well-Maintained Golf Course Complete with Driving Range Area, Clubhouse and Restaurant.  With a Little Love and Attention to Detail you can Make This One Perfect for Your Taste!  Don't Hesitate to Schedule Your Tour Today!!
